strapiSongs.title: Illusion of Control
strapiSongs.lyrics:
I cannot prove that I have the correct perspective
Everything that Iâ€™m doing could be wrong
All the thoughts in my mind may be deceiving
And my time on this earth may not be long

We have lost everything that we could believe in
Sold it all for illusion of control
Through the years I was searching for an answer
And in the darkness, I have heard the call
strapiSongs.credits: Written and recorded by Victor Fisher on June 27, 2023.
strapiSongs.description: A song about intuition. This is the first one I wrote in standard tuning.
